{"tid":2261388,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"旅遊保險不包武肺","createTime":"2020-10-28T09:29:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T00:26:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f59afbd01be00ef034228321651b28eecad6612f","tid":2261388,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T09:29:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201028/UKZO2YHYL5FPJIKNPESTTBTFTU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201028%2FUKZO2YHYL5FPJIKNPESTTBTFTU%2F&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7DsAEF7kNGMxk903cO3jeS8%3D&h=f759ea60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201028%2FUKZO2YHYL5FPJIKNPESTTBTFTU%2F&h=1a3a60e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201028/UKZO2YHYL5FPJIKNPESTTBTFTU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄 <br />\n<br />\n旅遊保險不包武肺<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rNNoc5BGNASXefgZy_2_dZSjLPc=/819x594/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NPCDOJ7S2JHGNHEUXP2ZD2INZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrNNoc5BGNASXefgZy_2_dZSjLPc%3D%2F819x594%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNPCDOJ7S2JHGNHEUXP2ZD2INZA.jpg&h=0ee2f47b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■旅發局近日舉辦「賞你遊香港」活動。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】商經局早前宣佈旅行社若舉辦本地旅行團，須為所有團友購買包含武漢肺炎保障的本地旅遊保險。不過，旅發局「賞你遊香港」活動中，由旅行社提供的本地旅行團，其旅遊保險賠償沒有寫明是否包含武漢肺炎。記者以顧客身份致電其中兩間旅行社查詢，兩間旅行社均表明不包武漢肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：睇科學館 中環扶手梯 口罩廠  悶行市區 旅發hea搞賞你遊<br />\n<br />\n專業旅運營辦的賞你遊香港旅行團，行程包括南生圍、紅樹林及雀鳥天堂，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n名單僅21團未達標<br />\n<br />\n佳天美香港有限公司則沒有在網頁上寫明有否包含保險，記者向職員查詢，對方稱「（旅行團）有提供旅遊保險，但唔包武漢肺炎，係普通交通意外（保險）」。<br />\n<br />\n旅發局上周公佈賞你遊香港計劃時，聲稱會提供接近50個由不同本地旅行社。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"817e3b8b0ce7733a4310416240c533c62ec666b9","tid":2261388,"uid":343977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T23:49:56.000Z","msg":"包武肺包到你生定死都包<br />\n好似真係得油王航空先包<br />\n中左比錢醫你 瓜左都保埋身後事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"767ad302e8a87f34bd6ca42cd0a55ed9d4ff3075","tid":2261388,"uid":278089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T00:26:20.000Z","msg":"正常，武肺係未知病毒，保險公司好難評估中咗之後需要幾多錢去醫，所以無保險係正常嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}